<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV1">
<l>pūnilāya vaintumāyp puṉaṟkaṇniṉṟa nāṉkumāyt</l>
<l>tīnilāya mūṉṟumāyc ciṟantakā liraṇṭumāy</l>
<l>mīnilāya toṉṟumāki vēṟuvēṟu taṉmaiyāy</l>
<l>nīnilāya vaṇṇaniṉṉai yārniṉaikka vallarē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Who is capable of understanding You [and] the way You stand [in all],</l>
<l rend="indent">Becoming the five [properties] that pervade the earth [element],</l>
<l rend="indent">becoming the four [properties] that abide in water,</l>
<l rend="indent">becoming the three [properties] that pervade fire,</l>
<l rend="indent">becoming the two [properties] in the eminent wind,</l>
<l rend="indent">becoming the one [property] that pervades the sky,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] becoming the various different essences [in them].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
